FlattenedCompoundField is a BusinessClass
    owned by repository
    store using com.lawson.rdtech.framework.repository.FlattenedCompoundFieldStorage

    Ontology
    	part of BusinessField
    		relative key is FullName is LPLName

    Patterns
    	implements ReadOnly
    	disable UniqueID

	Context Fields
		BusinessAction

    Persistent Fields
    	Type					is a BusinessFieldType
    	IsNamedType				is Boolean
            default label is "NamedType"
    	NamedType				is LPLName
    	ExtendedType			is a BusinessExtendedType
    	RepresentationType 		is a BusinessFieldRepresentationType
    	Size					is Numeric size 4
    	DecimalSize				is Numeric size 2
    	IsHiddenFrameworkField 	is Boolean
        	default label is "HiddenFrameworkField"
        FullSQLName				is LPLName
        IsValidForColumnar		is Boolean
            default label is "ValidForColumnar"
        HasParentTransient		is Boolean
        	default label is "MemberOfTransientField"
        HasParentContext		is Boolean
        	default label is "MemberOfContextField"
        
  	Conditions
  		IsOrInTransient
  		    default label is untranslatable
  			when (Type.Transient or HasParentTransient)
  		
  		IsOrInContext
  		    default label is untranslatable
  			when (Type.Context or HasParentContext)

    	    
